<item>
            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-1877] Malformed ACL Id can crash server with skipACL=yes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-1877</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Because of the way fixupACL is written in PrepRequestProcessor, a request that feeds in an ACL with null members in the Id will cause a server with skipACL=yes to crash.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A patch will be provided that re-introduces checks for well-formed ACLs even if skipACL is enabled.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
